    <item>
      <title>马克龙试图在政治混乱中重建法国政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/macron-says-he-will-serve-out-remainder-of-his-term-until-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将于周五会见主要政界人士，以组建新政府。此前一天，这位法国总统承诺完成其剩余任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/macron-says-he-will-serve-out-remainder-of-his-term-until-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 19:20:25 GMT</pubDate>
